#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:0
msgid "# triton.language.make_tensor_descriptor"
msgstr "# triton.language.make_tensor_descriptor"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:2
msgid "## 1. OP 概述"
msgstr "## 1. OP Overview"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:4
msgid ""
"简介：创建张量描述符对象\n"
"原型（Triton3.4.0版本）：\n"
msgstr ""
"Introduction: Create a tensor descriptor object\n"
"Prototype (Triton 3.4.0 version):\n"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:6
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"triton.language.make_tensor_descriptor(\n"
"    base: tensor,\n"
"    shape: List[tensor],\n"
"    strides: List[tensor],\n"
"    block_shape: List[constexpr],\n"
"    _semantic=None\n"
") -> tensor_descriptor\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:8
msgid "## 2. OP 规格"
msgstr "## 2. OP Specification"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:10
msgid "### 2.1 参数说明"
msgstr "### 2.1 Parameter Description"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:12
msgid ""
"| 参数名           | 类型                | 说明                                                             |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `base`        | `tensor`          | 张量的基指针                                                      |\n"
"| `shape`       | `List[tensor]`    | 张量的形状                                                        |\n"
"| `strides`     | `List[tensor]`    | 张量各维度的步长列表，约束如下：- 前面的维度必须是 16 字节的整数倍- 最后一维必须是连续存储的 |\n"
"| `block_shape` | `List[constexpr]` | 从全局内存加载 / 存储的块的形状                                              |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | 保留参数，暂不支持外部调用                                                |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Parameter Name | Type                | Description                                                                 |\n"
"| ------------- | ----------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------- |\n"
"| `base`        | `tensor`          | Base pointer of the tensor                                                 |\n"
"| `shape`       | `List[tensor]`    | Shape of the tensor                                                        |\n"
"| `strides`     | `List[tensor]`    | Stride list for each dimension of the tensor, with the following constraints: - The preceding dimensions must be integer multiples of 16 bytes - The last dimension must be contiguous in memory |\n"
"| `block_shape` | `List[constexpr]` | Shape of the block loaded from / stored to global memory                   |\n"
"| `_semantic`   | -                 | Reserved parameter; external calls are not supported for now               |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:14
msgid ""
"返回值：\n"
"`tensor_descriptor`：张量描述符对象（不可直接进行算术运算，需配合 `load` / `store` 使用）\n"
msgstr ""
"Return value:  \n"
"`tensor_descriptor`: A tensor descriptor object (cannot be directly used for arithmetic operations; must be used with `load` / `store`).\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:16
msgid "### 2.2 支持规格"
msgstr "### 2.2 Supported Specifications"

