msgid "结论：在 Shape 方面，GPU 与 Ascend 平台无差异，均支持 1 至 5 维张量。"
msgstr "Conclusion: In terms of shape, there is no difference between GPU and Ascend platforms, both supporting 1 to 5-dimensional tensors."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:28
msgid "### 2.3 特殊限制说明"
msgstr "### 2.3 Special Limitations"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:30
msgid "> 相对社区能力缺失且无法实现"
msgstr "Relative community capability is lacking and cannot be achieved."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:32
msgid "结论：Ascend 对比 GPU 缺失uint16、uint32、uint64的支持能力（硬件限制）。"
msgstr "Conclusion: Ascend lacks support for uint16, uint32, and uint64 compared to GPU (hardware limitation)."

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:34
msgid ""
"| 差异点                     | 描述                                                         | 解决途径                                               |\n"
"| -------------------------- | ------------------------------------------------------------ | ------------------------------------------------------ |\n"
"| 绑定使用限制               | `make_tensor_descriptor` / `load_tensor_descriptor` / `store_tensor_descriptor` 需配套使用，不能与 `tl.load()` / `tl.store()` 混用。 | 升级至 Triton 3.4.0 版本同步上游函数(如 `cast` )可解决 |\n"
"| 不支持`padding_option`入参 | 当前社区主线分支新增`padding_option`入参，用于越界元素填充策略。 | 可软件开发支持                                         |\n"
"| Triton 版本兼容性          | Triton 3.2.0 存在部分函数（如 `cast` ）的兼容性问题。建议升级 Triton版本至 3.4.0 来修复绑定限制。 | 升级至 Triton 3.4.0                                    |\n"
msgstr ""
"| Difference | Description | Solution |\n"
"| ----------- | ----------- | -------- |\n"
"| Binding usage restrictions | `make_tensor_descriptor` / `load_tensor_descriptor` / `store_tensor_descriptor` must be used together and cannot be mixed with `tl.load()` / `tl.store()`. | Upgrading to Triton 3.4.0 to synchronize upstream functions (such as `cast`) can resolve this. |\n"
"| `padding_option` parameter not supported | The current community main branch has added the `padding_option` parameter for out-of-bounds element padding strategies. | Software development support is available. |\n"
"| Triton version compatibility | Triton 3.2.0 has compatibility issues with some functions (such as `cast`). It is recommended to upgrade the Triton version to 3.4.0 to fix the binding restrictions. | Upgrade to Triton 3.4.0 |\n"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:36
msgid "### 2.4 使用方法"
msgstr "### 2.4 Usage"

#. type: text
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:38
msgid "以下示例实现了对输入张量 `x` 做就地绝对值计算："
msgstr "The following example implements an in-place absolute value calculation on the input tensor `x`:"

#. type: code
#: docs/zh/triton_api/Memory_Pointer_Ops/make_tensor_descriptor.md:40
msgid ""
"```python\n"
"@triton.jit\n"
"def inplace_abs(in_out_ptr, M, N, M_BLOCK: tl.constexpr, N_BLOCK: tl.constexpr):\n"
"    # 创建张量描述符\n"
"    desc = tl.make_tensor_descriptor(\n"
"        in_out_ptr,\n"
"        shape=[M, N],\n"
"        strides=[N, 1],\n"
"        block_shape=[M_BLOCK, N_BLOCK],\n"
"    )\n"
" # 计算当前线程对应的偏移量\n"
"    moffset = tl.program_id(0) * M_BLOCK\n"
"    noffset = tl.program_id(1) * N_BLOCK\n"
" # 加载数据，计算绝对值，存储结果\n"
"    value = desc.load([moffset, noffset])\n"
"    desc.store([moffset, noffset], tl.abs(value))\n"
"## 初始化张量\n"
"M, N = 256, 256\n"
"x = torch.randn(M, N, device=\"npu\")\n"
"## 配置块大小和网格\n"
"M_BLOCK, N_BLOCK = 32, 32\n"
"grid = (M // M_BLOCK, N // N_BLOCK)\n"
"inplace_abs[grid](x, M, N, M_BLOCK, N_BLOCK)\n"
"```\n"
msgstr ""

